{"tid":837473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港媒：北京似已做好與美國攤牌準備","createTime":"2018-09-26T11:38:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T05:27:47.000Z","uid":141151,"like":203,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":97,"replies":[{"pid":"84457bb7352ae45305ea21d56b44910b3c09ce5e","tid":837473,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T11:38:39.000Z","msg":"港媒：北京似已做好與美國攤牌準備<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/10814/3387741\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F10814%2F3387741&d=Df%2F4XjLza5srvzb%2B%2BQj%2Fb7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=8d4c826e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/10814/3387741</a><br />\n<br />\n香港明報今天刊登短評，猜測中國可能已經做好與美國攤牌的準備。<br />\n<br />\n短評指出，在美國對2000億美元中國商品加徵關稅生效之際，中國政府發表「中美經貿摩擦白皮書」，是貿易戰開打以來，中方對美國指摘最全面的回應。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">昨天，中國多個部門高官又一起召開記者會，宣稱拒絕美方「把刀架在脖子上」的談判。同日，中國又拒絕美國軍艦進入香港。</span><br />\n<br />\n短評並指出，中國外交部長王毅昨天在紐約出席聯合國大會期間的連串行動，外界較少注意。<br />\n<br />\n短評轉述新華社報導指出，王毅先後會見了10多名各國外長，只有見英國和澳洲外長時強調「應約」，即對方主動約見，似含對兩國附和美國的警惕性。<br />\n<br />\n短評表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">王毅的重頭戲是會見美中關係全國委員會、美中貿易全國委員會的負責人，而非會見美國國務卿。期間，他批評美方在新一輪對話前夕啟動更大規模單邊徵稅行動。<br />\n<br />\n短評指出，自從中國與美國展開貿易戰以來，中方一直忍口不出惡言，但這一輪攻勢，話都說得很重，不知是否意味做好了（與美國）攤牌的準備。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f68e9d0f919aa24df452b2bd389c345c86859b9","tid":837473,"uid":30169,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T11:40:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4ada19f14b514c8f6208cb10715fc5cbffdbbc7","tid":837473,"uid":39698,"like":42,"dislike":2,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T11:42:06.000Z","msg":"曬佢冷<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a40a7af2897623c9da3d166f0e6a3038ed8457d","tid":837473,"uid":134736,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T11:43:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開打啦"},{"pid":"b7d02b974c41d3e9b53289d50a50ecb09cc32ea0","tid":837473,"uid":32675,"like":74,"dislike":1,"score":73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T11:44:00.000Z","msg":"侵侵:全面徵稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec60bfedeaa336c9c6821643e0762bfbd0e50d57","tid":837473,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T11:44:20.000Z","msg":"即係點？"},{"pid":"d2aebe7e179946c1b0df3097d2673361ded4b33f","tid":837473,"uid":176442,"like":147,"dislike":4,"score":143,"quote":{"pid":"ec60bfedeaa336c9c6821643e0762bfbd0e50d57","tid":837473,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T11:44:20.000Z","msg":"即係點？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T11:44:45.000Z","msg":"認輸"},{"pid":"9686bb28323e01891aac1f1d78b376216454e873","tid":837473,"uid":127988,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T11:45:07.000Z","msg":"總之中國又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wink.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea7c8c11455bf96de44efa0c768341b2538696b8","tid":837473,"uid":73942,"like":96,"dislike":1,"score":95,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T11:45:19.000Z","msg":"維妮快d打鳩美國佬啦，想睇下贏國幾大鑊全牲"},{"pid":"b09278cacf295a26a9a765a7248c3f002d06d445","tid":837473,"uid":51665,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T11:45:30.000Z","msg":"WW3 is coming<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85344820361a99db7949c8b3ea37bbb596dc1fbd","tid":837473,"uid":132587,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T11:45:37.000Z","msg":"跪住攤<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c77914999a018d71c4c1eecc8d455b640b8591d","tid":837473,"uid":127988,"like":13,"dislike